```

<h2>Javascript</h2>
<p>Create a `Graphic` instance</p>
```
    var mygraphic = new Y.Graphic({render:"#mygraphiccontainer"});
```

<p>Use the `addShape` method to create an ellipse.</p>
```
    var myellipse = mygraphic.addShape({
        type: "ellipse",
        fill: {
            color: "#9aa"
        },
        stroke: {
            weight: 2,
            color: "#000"
        }
    });
```
